            <div class="post-content gt-c-content-color-first">
                <p>最开始</p>
<p>$ git push -u origin main</p>
<p>output:</p>
<p>remote: Permission to ViteMux/repo.git denied to Olduser.</p>
<p>fatal: unable to access ‘<a href="https://github.com/ViteMux/repo.git/&#39;">https://github.com/ViteMux/repo.git/&#39;</a>: The requested URL returned error: 403</p>
<p>我设置了local的username，但是却显示了旧用户被拒绝请求了，所以我以为是上一次的commit的author还是旧用户</p>
<p>所以我尝试：</p>
<p>$ git commit –amend –reset-author</p>
<p>结果还是一样，最后在 <a href="https://www.blogger.com/blog/post/edit/3258410905752786662/7124892052163434745#">stackoverflow</a> 中找到了方法</p>
<p><a href="https://www.blogger.com/blog/post/edit/3258410905752786662/7124892052163434745#"><img src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj0wbUoiTtF090WOtkX1mqVJYhs0KpLCoKEfweTLqsbktGKREfV1UkCd4TAvF2lj6fIXYiVINV-hVD3-Yz4aly0MIvMmwWS1JcKBVBhwTveoF56wKhbrSr8r39dBKBFGMjr1Ql-eNdNwbVv-lTBCRA_1cAzB_ZkYpudXcWlsAWak-u7nu0uTJfqNFHjrUaK/s320/%E6%8D%95%E8%8E%B7.PNG" alt></a></p>
